{"name": "Community Crisis Center Inc.", "alternate_name": "", "description": "Please have your ID ready when you pull into the driveway. Let us us know if you are already registered with Link2Feed. You can preregister here: https://mdfoodbank.link2feed.com/

Walk-up clients are welcome and will be directed a safe area to the side of the driveway.  The building is not open to the public.

If you need clothing, please fill out our Clothing Request Form here- https://communitycrisiscenterinc.org/?page_id=924. Allow 10 days processing time to complete your request. Please only submit one clothing request form per household per month.  

Please call 410-526-7111 ext. 310 in the event of inclement weather.
